{"tid":1520644,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌，原來終極一戰，係講港共呀，哈？","createTime":"2019-08-31T01:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:23:58.000Z","uid":32051,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0619c23000766d53f09228f888e6d6c23bcd26c","tid":1520644,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T01:57:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咁你收硬皮都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日鳩拉一眾議員，socalled政治明星。今日又ddos連登，再出個弱鳩智警犬講乜撚野行街睇花都唔撚得。<br />\n加埋黨鐵配合你，自己搞到港島變死城，有閪用咩。<br />\n我出去行街，要去點都去到；唔去行街，你狗共搞到人地做唔成生意，又唔撚關我事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地咁想玩焦土，咪玩撚飽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當今日無人出街消費。<br />\n挑，你避到初一，避到十五咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞一場大龍鳳最後乜鳩都做唔到，你點同黨解釋呀？？拖到開學呀？！<br />\n開學佢地就玩另一條戰線架啦，要你班狗警全面收皮。<br />\n<br />\n黨出左咁多黑客幫你地攻擊擊連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚你地無貨交呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45709d79eb60b79e6e1cbc63c782aaef81d31b20","tid":1520644,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7z